Setup
=====
$ python3 -m pip install --user qmk
$ export PATH="$PATH:$HOME/.local/bin" 
$ qmk setup -H ~/sources/qmk_firmware

Copy the keymap directories into the QMK tree.

Usage
=====
$ qmk <command> -kb <keyboard> -km <keymap>

For example:

$ qmk compile -kb ymdk/yd60mq -km clamiax
$ qmk flash -kb ymdk/yd60mq -km clamiax
